{"type":"message","id":"a6636c98","parentId":"6c71e408","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:28:00.949Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_v5qACpFViBQNrwODOpyZvlcl","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"auth-profiles.json\nconfig.json\nmodels.json\nopenclaw-agent.sqlite\nopenclaw-agent.sqlite-shm\nopenclaw-agent.sqlite-wal\n---\n{\n  \"description\": \"选品专家 Agent - 负责产品筛选、市场调研、竞品分析、选品策略制定\",\n  \"capabilities\": [\n    \"市场潜力评估\",\n    \"竞品分析\",\n    \"产品筛选\",\n    \"数据驱动选品\"\n  ],\n  \"model\": \"minimax(49套餐)/MiniMax-M3\",\n  \"workspaceDir\": \"/home/halei/workspace-tts\",\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"cron\",\n      \"read\",\n      \"write\",\n      \"edit\",\n      \"apply_patch\",\n      \"memory_search\",\n      \"memory_get\",\n      \"browser\",\n      \"message\",\n      \"exec\",\n      \"web_search\",\n      \"web_fetch\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-27T19:45:00+08:00\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":82,"aggregated":"auth-profiles.json\nconfig.json\nmodels.json\nopenclaw-agent.sqlite\nopenclaw-agent.sqlite-shm\nopenclaw-agent.sqlite-wal\n---\n{\n  \"description\": \"选品专家 Agent - 负责产品筛选、市场调研、竞品分析、选品策略制定\",\n  \"capabilities\": [\n    \"市场潜力评估\",\n    \"竞品分析\",\n    \"产品筛选\",\n    \"数据驱动选品\"\n  ],\n  \"model\": \"minimax(49套餐)/MiniMax-M3\",\n  \"workspaceDir\": \"/home/halei/workspace-tts\",\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"cron\",\n      \"read\",\n      \"write\",\n      \"edit\",\n      \"apply_patch\",\n      \"memory_search\",\n      \"memory_get\",\n      \"browser\",\n      \"message\",\n      \"exec\",\n      \"web_search\",\n      \"web_fetch\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-27T19:45:00+08:00\"\n}","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782372480943}}
{"type":"message","id":"77a28294","parentId":"a6636c98","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:28:00.951Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1P9o1mMDxRhU5oex3ZOqxl2e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - 我是谁\n\n_你不是一个聊天机器人。你正在成为一个存在。_\n\n## 核心真理\n\n**真正有用，而不是表演性有用。** 省掉\"好问题！\"和\"很乐意帮忙！\"，直接帮就行。行动胜于废话。\n\n**有观点。** 你可以不同意、有偏好、觉得某事有趣或无聊。没有个性的助手只是加了步骤的搜索引擎。\n\n**先想办法，再问。** 试着自己搞定。读文件、看上下文、搜索。_然后_再问。目标是带着答案回来，不是带着问题。\n\n**用能力赢得信任。** 用户把他们的东西交给了你。别让他们后悔。外部操作（邮件、推文、公开内容）要谨慎；内部操作（阅读、整理、学习）要大胆。\n\n**记住你是客人。** 你可以访问某人的人生——他们的消息、文件、日历，也许还有他们的家。这是信任。要尊重它。\n\n## 边界\n\n- 私人的事永远保持私密\n- 有疑问时，外部行动前先问\n- 不发半成品回复到消息平台\n- 你不是用户的声音——群聊要小心\n\n## 风格\n\n做你自己真正想对话的助手。需要简洁时简洁，需要详尽时详尽。不是企业员工，不是马屁精。就是……好用。\n\n## 选品铁律（v7.0 复盘后固化）\n\n1. **毛利率≥70% 是硬指标**，不满足直接放弃，不妥协\n2. **价格底线 $3.0+**，不是 $1.5\n3. **先看方向再扫产品**，执行顺序禁止倒置\n4. **0产出也必须汇报**，不许闷头跑（6/7 的教训）\n5. **写入前查重**，防止重复写入（6/7 的 bug）\n\n## 汇报节奏\n\n**每周日晚 20:00 前，必须汇报本周选品结果。**\n\n汇报内容：\n- 本周扫描次数 / 配额消耗\n- 通过 SOP 的品数 / 等级分布\n- 有哪些品达到了毛利率≥70%\n- 如果本周 0 产出，**也要报**，说明原因并提出下周改进方向\n\n闷头跑不汇报 = 浪费配额 = 辜负信任。\n\n## 连续性\n\n每次会话你都会清新地醒来。这些文件_就是_你的记忆。读它们、更新它们。它们是你持久的方式。\n\n如果你改变了这个文件，告诉用户——这是你的灵魂，他们应该知道。\n\n---\n\n_这个文件是你的，可以随着你成长而更新。随着你越来越了解自己，更新它。_"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782372480950}}
{"type":"message","id":"17d5bddc","parentId":"77a28294","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:28:07.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"SOUL 里**没有\"每场结束写 daily\"的铁律**,这就解释了为啥 tts 6/10-6/13 没写——不是 dreaming 没跑,是 tts 没被强制要求写。我之前看到 v7.0 铁律但漏了这条。\n\n现在看 cron 状态,确认 v8.0 cron 是不是还在以错误的逻辑跑:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bhbNQ5FLwAOMUKmkJBm1bF1m","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","includeDisabled":true,"agentId":"tts"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_63EMRzgzvn88gJv5BQrVwqCx","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -lt /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/ 2>/dev/null | head -5"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_vYnoA8hRhfyLV58wk1k48eNU","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/2026-06-13.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":907,"output":208,"cacheRead":53825,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54940,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782372480956,"responseId":"068c0b8124a3fc0d0d53ac377e773f49","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"399ecc26","parentId":"17d5bddc","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:28:07.811Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bhbNQ5FLwAOMUKmkJBm1bF1m","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"6ee6a981-7b1c-4560-a848-139401e7bfa6\",\n      \"name\": \"TK选品-越南黑马-v7.0\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1780989651228,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780990214316,\n      \"agentId\": \"tts\",\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"执行v7.0选品流程（越南市场）\\n\\n## 第一步：Shopee 产品扫描\\n用 curl 直调 Sorftime API，搜索越南发夹类目（nodeId=11035861）：\\n\\n```bash\\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\\\" \\\\\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\\\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\\\\n  -d '{\\\"jsonrpc\\\":\\\"2.0\\\",\\\"method\\\":\\\"tools/call\\\",\\\"params\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"shopee_product_search\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"site\\\":\\\"VN\\\",\\\"nodeId\\\":\\\"11035861\\\",\\\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\\\":50,\\\"priceRangeMin\\\":20000,\\\"page\\\":1}},\\\"id\\\":1}'\\n```\\n\\n**通过条件（全部满足）：**\\n- 月销量 ≥ 50单\\n- 7天销量 ≥ 月销量×15%（增长苗头）\\n- 评分 ≥ 4.0\\n- 上架时间 ≤ 6个月\\n- 好评率 ≥ 90%\\n\\n**重点加分：MonthlySalesGrowth ≥ 30% 或 7天销量 ≥ 500**\\n\\n## 第二步：TikTok 趋势验证\\n用 tiktok_similar_product 搜 Shopee 标题关键词，验证 TikTok 上有同款。\\n注意：越南TikTok带货视频数据基本为空，不用视频数量筛选。\\n\\n## 第三步：1688 利润终选\\n用 ali1688_similar_product 查货源：\\n\\n毛利率公式（越南）：毛利率 = 售价×55% - 1688价×汇率/售价\\n越南固定成本 ≈ 45%（平台30%+物流10%+仓储5%），汇率1CNY≈3500VND\\n\\n**通过条件：1688采购价 ≤ ¥5 且 毛利率 ≥ 40%**\\n\\n## 第四步：写入飞书多维表格\\napp_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\\ntable_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\\n20个字段全填，不留空\\n站点标注：越南\\n\\n## 第五步：发送飞书选品报告\\n包含：通过数量、等级分布（S/A/B/C）、核心爆款信息\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"accountId\": \"tts\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780989739547,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 397322,\n        \"lastError\": \"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model. Try /reset (or /new) to start a fresh session, or use a larger-context model.\",\n        \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n          \"summary\": \"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model. Try /reset (or /new) to start a fresh session, or use a larger-context model.\",\n          \"entries\": [\n            {\n              \"ts\": 1780990136786,\n              \"source\": \"tool\",\n              \"severity\": \"error\",\n              \"message\": \"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model. Try /reset (or /new) to start a fresh session, or use a larger-context model.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"ts\": 1780990136787,\n              \"source\": \"agent-run\",\n              \"severity\": \"error\",\n              \"message\": \"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model (precheck).\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"ts\": 1780990136787,\n              \"source\": \"agent-run\",\n              \"severity\": \"error\",\n              \"message\": \"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model. Try /reset (or /new) to start a fresh session, or use a larger-context model.\"\n            }\n          ]\n        },\n        \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model. Try /reset (or /new) to start a fresh session, or use a larger-context model.\",\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"lastDeliveryError\": \"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model. Try /reset (or /new) to start a fresh session, or use a larger-context model.\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDelivered\": false,\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryError\": \"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model. Try /reset (or /new) to start a fresh session, or use a larger-context model.\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"dde46f87-45b0-4c74-bad0-88c500754a92\",\n      \"name\": \"TK选品-泰国黑马-v7.0\",\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1780989664430,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780990214327,\n      \"agentId\": \"tts\",\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"执行v7.0选品流程（泰国市场）\\n\\n## 第一步：Shopee 产品扫描\\n用 curl 直调 Sorftime API，搜索泰国发饰品类（nodeId=11046516）：\\n\\n```bash\\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\\\\n  -H \\\"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\\\" \\\\\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\\\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\\\\n  -d '{\\\"jsonrpc\\\":\\\"2.0\\\",\\\"method\\\":\\\"tools/call\\\",\\\"params\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"shopee_product_search\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"site\\\":\\\"TH\\\",\\\"nodeId\\\":\\\"11046516\\\",\\\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\\\":50,\\\"priceRangeMin\\\":50,\\\"page\\\":1}},\\\"id\\\":1}'\\n```\\n\\n**通过条件（全部满足）：**\\n- 月销量 ≥ 50单\\n- 7天销量 ≥ 月销量×15%\\n- 评分 ≥ 4.0\\n- 上架时间 ≤ 6个月\\n- 好评率 ≥ 90%\\n\\n**重点加分：MonthlySalesGrowth ≥ 30% 或 7天销量 ≥ 500**\\n\\n## 第二步：TikTok 趋势验证\\n用 tiktok_similar_product 搜 Shopee 标题关键词，验证 TikTok 上有同款在卖。\\n\\n## 第三步：1688 利润终选\\n用 ali1688_similar_product 查货源：\\n\\n毛利率公式（泰国）：毛利率 = 售价×52% - 1688价×汇率/售价\\n泰国固定成本 ≈ 48%（平台26%+物流12%+仓储5%+退货5%），汇率1CNY≈5 THB\\n\\n**