{"type":"message","id":"2e8b1735","parentId":"923eaf55","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:30:29.600Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到 ✅ 那 profile 名就用 **Heat Up Glow - 时尚配件**。\n\n你点 Chrome 卡片里的\"登录 Chrome\",登录账号后我这边就能用这个 profile 名操作(以后 `browser` 工具会一直用这个家)。\n\n几个跟你确认下:\n\n1. **登录的 Google 账号** —— 是你平时已经在用的那个(里面已经有 TikTok Seller / Shopee / 1688 的密码保存了),还是新开一个专门给\"Heat Up Glow\"用?\n2. **登录完跟我说一声**,我再继续动那个 5 步计划(SOUL + daily + cron + MEMORY)\n\n[[reply_to_current"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":649,"output":136,"cacheRead":58496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59281,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782372619801,"responseId":"068c0c0c3ccbd1432da3998a87f3d28c","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
