{"type":"message","id":"6a978ae0","parentId":"a24cbf92","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:31:26.196Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"SOUL 改完 ✅ 现在补 6/10-6/13 三个 daily:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_019efdb0d6b17cf3a47d405f","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/2026-06-10.md","content":"# 2026-06-10\n\n## 今日概要\n**店铺定位日**。HALEI 明确发饰是主营类目，越南+泰国市场。\n\n## 关键决策\n- 主营：发夹/发圈/头饰（不换类目）\n- 市场：越南（VN）+ 泰国（TH）双站点\n- v7.0 流程继续跑（毛利率≥70%、价格底线$3.0 仍是当时的标准）\n\n## 产出\n- v7.0 cron 已部署（越南+泰国各一条，0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *）\n- 越南站发夹 nodeId=11035861、泰国站发饰 nodeId=11046516\n\n## 待办\n- [ ] 观察 v7.0 几次 cron 的实际产出\n- [ ] Sorftime API 配额监控（5/27 已耗尽过一次，6/3 充值 30000 次）"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_019efdb0d6b17cf3a47d406f","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/2026-06-11.md","content":"# 2026-06-11\n\n## 今日概要\n**无主动操作日**。v7.0 cron 在跑，但 tts 没主动产出新决策。\n\n## 关键事实\n- v7.0 cron（越南/泰国）持续触发\n- 当日没有与 HALEI 的关键对话\n- Sorftime 配额消耗中\n\n## 待办\n- [ ] 跟进 v7.0 cron 产出情况\n- [ ] 复盘选品标准是否过严（毛利率≥70%）"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_019efdb0d6b17cf3a47d4079","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/2026-06-12.md","content":"# 2026-06-12\n\n## 今日概要\n**v7.0 cron 持续报错日**。晚间 cron 触发 v7.0 越南选品扫描。\n\n## 关键事实\n- 当日 cron 多次报 \"AI service overloaded\" 或上下文溢出\n- 越南站能拿到数据，但通过率极低（毛利率≥70% 卡掉绝大多数候选）\n- 泰国站 `tiktok_similar_product` API 报错\n- 6/12 cron session 文件在 `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/tts/sessions/`，但 tts 没主动收尾\n\n## 产出\n- 无\n\n## 教训\n- v7.0 标准可能过严，毛利率≥70% 让通过数极低\n- \"AI service overloaded\" 反复出现 → 模型压力或配额问题\n\n## 待办\n- [ ] HALEI 反馈选品标准问题\n- [ ] 评估调整 SOP 算法"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":153,"output":681,"cacheRead":60288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61122,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782372664637,"responseId":"068c0c38ec179459a873fe233104bca6","responseModel":"MiniMax-M