{"type":"message","id":"2f2570f3","parentId":"d0f56b9d","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:33:07.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"MEMORY.md 更新完 ✅ 现在写 tts 今天的 daily:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_019efdb263ab71c3a1212dc6","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/memory/2026-06-25.md","content":"# 2026-06-25\n\n## 今日概要\n**大总管 HALEI 主持的系统性修复日**。tts 的记忆系统、SOP 算法、cron 调度全部重新对齐。\n\n## 关键决策（来自 HALEI/大总管）\n- **店铺名确认**：Heat Up Glow - 时尚配件-发饰\n- **主营类目锁定**：发饰（发夹/发圈/头饰），不换类目\n- **v7.0 cron 全部删除**（毛利率≥70%硬卡导致 0 产出）\n- **v8.0 cron 上线**：候选池模式，扫描→评分→推送 HALEI 审核→人工选品\n\n## 产出\n- ✅ SOUL.md 新增\"记忆铁律\"（每场结束/cron 完成必须写 daily）\n- ✅ SOUL.md 新增\"店铺身份\"段落（不发饰品类问\"经营什么类目\"）\n- ✅ 补写 6/10-6/13 三个 daily.md（之前完全空白）\n- ✅ 删除 v7.0 cron（6ee6a981 越南 / dde46f87 泰国）\n- ✅ 新建 v8.0 cron：\n  - 越南黑马-v8.0（id: d6ea3ee4）：0 9,12,15,18 * * *\n  - 泰国黑马-v8.0（id: 91574622）：0 10,13,16,19 * * *\n- ✅ MEMORY.md 更新（店铺身份/Cron 任务/已知限制）\n\n## 关键修复点\n- v7.0 cron 报\"Context overflow: prompt too large for the model\"→ v8.0 提示词精简到 ~1.2KB（原 ~1.5KB）\n- v7.0 算法（毛利≥70%）和市场结构不匹配→ v8.0 改为\"潜力款宽进 + 后端结构实现利润\"\n- tts 6/10-6/13 完全没写 daily → 加 SOUL 铁律强制要求\n\n## 待办\n- [ ] 观察 v8.0 cron 16:00 首次跑的结果\n- [ ] 排查 tiktok_similar_product / ali1688_similar_product API 报错（6/13至今未修）\n- [ ] HALEI 确认潜力评分权重倾向（当前用\"价格带宽\"代替\"TK 验证\"占位）\n- [ ] 飞书多维表写入权限复查（v8.0 不直接写，需 HALEI 审核后人工触发）"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_019efdb263ab71c3a1212dd1","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"plan":[{"step":"改 tts SOUL.md,加'每场结束写 daily'铁律","status":"completed"},{"step":"补 6/10-6/13 三个 daily.md","status":"completed"},{"step":"删 v7.0 cron(越南+泰国)","status":"completed"},{"step":"写 v8.0 cron(越南+泰国)","status":"completed"},{"step":"更新 tts MEMORY.md(店铺名/主营/v8.0)","status":"completed"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":150,"output":828,"cacheRead":70400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71378,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason