{"type":"message","id":"b7f0aec9","parentId":"798db140","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:33:38.235Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"全部搞定 ✅ 总结一下做了什么:\n\n| 步骤 | 状态 | 备注 |\n|---|---|---|\n| ① tts SOUL.md 加\"记忆铁律\"+\"店铺身份\" | ✅ | 改灵魂已通知 |\n| ② 补 6/10-6/13 三个 daily | ✅ | 之前完全空白 |\n| ③ 删 v7.0 cron(越南+泰国) | ✅ | 两条全删 |\n| ④ 建 v8.0 cron(越南+泰国) | ✅ | 越南 9/12/15/18、泰国 10/13/16/19 |\n| ⑤ 更新 tts MEMORY.md | ✅ | 店铺身份/Cron/权重/限制 |\n| ⑥ 写 tts 今日 daily | ✅ | `memory/2026-06-25.md` |\n| ⑦ 写我的今日 daily | ✅ | 反思了\"我误解桌面\"那个波折 |\n\n**接下来观察项:**\n- 今天 16:00 是 v8.0 cron 首次实战,我会盯着\n- 如果跑成功,会按计划向 HALEI 推候选池飞书消息\n- Chrome 这边你登录完后,我下次 `browser` 调用会用 `Heat Up Glow - 时尚配件-发饰` profile\n\n需要我现在再帮你检查什么,还是等 16:00 跑结果?\n\n[[reply_to_current"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":66,"output":298,"cacheRead":72064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72428,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782372810025,"responseId":"068c0ccae22fcdd2bef0e396418814b7","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
