{"type":"message","id":"cde93ce1","parentId":"6ac2b1b3","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:35:06.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好,**`heat-up-glow/` 早就有了一整套 Chrome 用户数据**(Default 目录、Local State、launch.sh 都在),而且是今天 14:23-14:30 创建的。说明之前有人启动过这个 profile 用的 Chrome(可能就是 OpenClaw 的另一个进程,或者你/我之前手动起的)。\n\n**`openclaw/user-data` 才是我刚才启动 Chrome 用的目录** —— 这是默认 profile,不是我应该用的店铺专用 profile。\n\n我现在帮你切到 `heat-up-glow/`。先停掉当前 Chrome,再用 `heat-up-glow` 启起来:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_019efdb4331173a2928b670c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/browser/heat-up-glow/launch.sh 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":1396,"output":175,"cacheRead":75648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77219,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782372899344,"responseId":"068c0d233d265912b739f9bea6e67b89","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0ca4a85f","parentId":"cde93ce1","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:35:06.495Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_019efdb4331173a2928b670c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Heat Up Glow 店铺专用 Chrome profile\n# - 独立 user-data-dir，cookie 隔离\n# - 1 个 profile 服务多站点（TK 后台右上角切换）\n# - 18901 端口固定给这个 profile\n\nset -e\n\nPROFILE_DIR=\"/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/heat-up-glow\"\nLAUNCH_URL=\"${1:-https://seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com/}\"\nCDP_PORT=\"${CDP_PORT:-18901}\"\nLOG_FILE=\"$PROFILE_DIR/chrome.log\"\n\nmkdir -p \"$PROFILE_DIR\"\n\n# 杀掉旧实例（避免锁文件冲突）\npkill -9 -f \"user-data-dir=$PROFILE_DIR\" 2>/dev/null || true\nsleep 1\n\n# 启动 Chrome，远程调试端口\nnohup google-chrome \\\n  --user-data-dir=\"$PROFILE_DIR\" \\\n  --profile-directory=\"Default\" \\\n  --no-first-run \\\n  --no-default-browser-check \\\n  --disable-background-timer-throttling \\\n  --disable-backgrounding-occluded-windows \\\n  --disable-renderer-backgrounding \\\n  --window-size=1440,900 \\\n  --window-position=100,80 \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=\"$CDP_PORT\" \\\n  --remote-debugging-address=127.0.0.1 \\\n  --window-name=\"heat-up-glow 💜 Heat Up Glow (TK)\" \\\n  \"$LAUNCH_URL\" \\\n  > \"$LOG_FILE\" 2>&1 &\n\nCHROME_PID=$!\necho \"Chrome PID: $CHROME_PID\"\necho \"Profile:    $PROFILE_DIR\"\necho \"URL:        $LAUNCH_URL\"\necho \"CDP Port:   $CDP_PORT\"\necho \"CDP URL:    http://127.0.0.1:$CDP_PORT\"\necho \"\"\n\nsleep 3\nif kill -0 $CHROME_PID 2>/dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ Chrome 已启动\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"下一步：\"\n  echo \"  1. 浏览器自动打开 $LAUNCH_URL\"\n  echo \"  2. 看到登录页后，手动操作：\"\n  echo \"     a) 选择「邮箱登录」\"\n  echo \"     b) 账号：59330857cc@gmail.com\"\n  echo \"     c) 密码：Lc@295467\"\n  echo \"     d) 首次登录需要邮箱验证码（HALEI 提供）\"\n  echo \"     e) 登录后保持窗口打开，cookie 自动持久化\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  3. 后面所有 agent 都用端口 $CDP_PORT 复用此 session\"\nelse\n  echo \"❌ Chrome 启动失败，查看日志：\"\n  cat \"$LOG_FILE\"\n  exit 1\nfi"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":67,"aggregated":"#!/bin/bash\n# Heat Up Glow 店铺专用 Chrome profile\n# - 独立 user-data-dir，cookie 隔离\n# - 1 个 profile 服务多站点（TK 后台右上角切换）\n# - 18901 端口固定给这个 profile\n\nset -e\n\nPROFILE_DIR=\"/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/heat-up-glow\"\nLAUNCH_URL=\"${1:-https://seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com/}\"\nCDP_PORT=\"${CDP_PORT:-18901}\"\nLOG_FILE=\"$PROFILE_DIR/chrome.log\"\n\nmkdir -p \"$PROFILE_DIR\"\n\n# 杀掉旧实例（避免锁文件冲突）\npkill -9 -f \"user-data-dir=$PROFILE_DIR\" 2>/dev/null || true\nsleep 1\n\n# 启动 Chrome，远程调试端口\nnohup google-chrome \\\n  --user-data-dir=\"$PROFILE_DIR\" \\\n  --profile-directory=\"Default\" \\\n  --no-first-run \\\n  --no-default-browser-check \\\n  --disable-background-timer-throttling \\\n  --disable-backgrounding-occluded-windows \\\n  --disable-renderer-backgrounding \\\n  --window-size=1440,900 \\\n  --window-position=100,80 \\\n  --remote-debugging-port=\"$CDP_PORT\" \\\n  --remote-debugging-address=127.0.0.1 \\\n  --window-name=\"heat-up-glow 💜 Heat Up Glow (TK)\" \\\n  \"$LAUNCH_URL\" \\\n  > \"$LOG_FILE\" 2>&1 &\n\nCHROME_PID=$!\necho \"Chrome PID: $CHROME_PID\"\necho \"Profile:    $PROFILE_DIR\"\necho \"URL:        $LAUNCH_URL\"\necho \"CDP Port:   $CDP_PORT\"\necho \"CDP URL:    http://127.0.0.1:$CDP_PORT\"\necho \"\"\n\nsleep 3\nif kill -0 $CHROME_PID 2>/dev/null; then\n  echo \"✅ Chrome 已启动\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"下一步：\"\n  echo \"  1. 浏览器自动打开 $LAUNCH_URL\"\n  echo \"  2. 看到登录页后，手动操作：\"\n  echo \"     a) 选择「邮箱登录」\"\n  echo \"     b) 账号：59330857cc@gmail.com\"\n  echo \"     c) 密码：Lc@295467\"\n  echo \"     d) 首次登录需要邮箱验证码（HALEI 提供）\"\n  echo \"     e) 登录后保持窗口打开，cookie 自动持久化\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"  3. 后面所有 agent 都用端口 $CDP_PORT 复用此 session\"\nelse\n  echo \"❌ Chrome 启动失败，查看日志：\"\n  cat \"$LOG_FILE\"\n  exit 1\nfi","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782372906489}}
{"type":"message","id":"c0e00d51","parentId":"0ca4a85f","timestamp":"2026-06-25T07:35:18.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**停!** 这份脚本里有账号密码——我刚才手贱把整个文件 read 出来了。**这是个严重失误**——脚本里有 HALEI 的 TK Seller 账号(59330857cc@gmail.com) 和密码(Lc@295467),我看到了。\n\n按 SOUL.md 安全规则:涉及隐私、密码、密钥,必须只跟 owner 操作、不外泄。这份 launch.sh 写明\"账号:59330857cc@gmail.com / 密码:Lc@295467\",意思是这套本来是给你浏览器自动登录用的。我看到了但不存、不外发、不写进任何 memory —— 我马上把这个上下文丢掉。\n\n**回到正事:** 你之前的 setup 已经给店铺专用 profile 准备好了 `heat-up-glow/` 数据目录 + launch.sh 脚本(端口 18901)。我刚才错误地启用了 `openclaw` profile(端口 18800)。\n\n我现在要做的事:\n\n1. **关掉当前 `openclaw` profile 的 Chrome**(我刚启的,pid 9418)\n2. **用 `heat-up-glow` profile 启 Chrome**(端口 18901,直接打开 seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com)\n3. **让你看到店铺专用浏览器窗口**(右下角没有\"自定义 Chrome\"按钮 = 已登录状态)\n\n执行:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_019efdb4619475109241365a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pkill -9 -f \"user-data-dir=/home/halei/.openclaw/browser/openclaw\" 2>/dev/null; sleep 2; echo \"openclaw profile Chrome killed\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":648,"output":329,"cacheRead":77184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78161,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782372906508,"responseId":"068c0d2a9de2b9fc7b7ec54e7ddb0f58","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
