{"type":"message","id":"c18ecbf8","parentId":"781d801a","timestamp":"2026-06-25T13:29:30.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"宿主 Chrome 10554 关了 ✅ 现在 `heat-up-glow` profile 没在宿主桌面上弹窗了。\n\n## 关于 opencli 你要的回答\n\n**你问的\"opencli 学习完后端脚本沉淀成 skill\" —— 答案:对。**\n\n**opencli**(独立安装的)的工作流就是:\n1. 启动**隔离 Chrome 实例**(不弹宿主窗口)\n2. 探索目标站点(DOM + 流程)\n3. 生成可执行脚本\n4. 沉淀成 skill 给后续 agent 用\n\n**但有个关键前提我之前漏说了**:opencli 通常跑在**隔离环境**,通过 CDP 端口远程控制,**不在你宿主桌面弹 Chrome 窗口**。我今天下午启动的方式(用宿主 `google-chrome` + launch.sh)违反了这个前提。\n\n## 现在怎么办?\n\n我需要确认两件事再动手:\n\n1. **opencli 在你机器上的真实路径/命令** —— 我之前以为它是 dreamina-cli,搞错了。我去看下是不是已经装在哪:\n2. **opencli 期望的\"隔离 Chrome\"启动方式** —— 是它自己起、还是我要先给它起一个无头 Chrome\n\n我先去找一下 opencli:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_019efef8ac2c77b3bb5061a9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which opencli 2>/dev/null; which open-cli 2>/dev/null; ls /usr/local/bin/open* 2>/dev/null; ls /opt/opencli* 2>/dev/null; find /home/halei -maxdepth 3 -name \"*opencli*\" 2>/dev/null | head -5; find /home/halei -maxdepth 3 -name \"*open-cli*\" 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":107,"output":372,"cacheRead":82432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82911,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782394160004,"responseId":"068c6030e08a147c63d7b1c4bb0a2d4a","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
