{"type":"message","id":"d8d6ab58","parentId":"b92dc3cb","timestamp":"2026-06-25T13:29:43.023Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_019efef8d75d72309f588bc4","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Usage: opencli browser <session> init [options] <name>\n\nGenerate adapter scaffold in ~/.opencli/clis/\n\nArguments:\n  name        Adapter name in site/command format (e.g. hn/top)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  display help for command\n\n  Update available: v1.8.1 → v1.8.4\n  Run: npm install -g @jackwener/opencli"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":744,"aggregated":"Usage: opencli browser <session> init [options] <name>\n\nGenerate adapter scaffold in ~/.opencli/clis/\n\nArguments:\n  name        Adapter name in site/command format (e.g. hn/top)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  display help for command\n\n  Update available: v1.8.1 → v1.8.4\n  Run: npm install -g @jackwener/opencli","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782394183021}}
{"type":"message","id":"95a1bbd5","parentId":"d8d6ab58","timestamp":"2026-06-25T13:29:51.553Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**关键信息**:\n\n1. ✅ **opencli 有 tiktok adapter**(comment, creator-videos, search 等),但是**没有 seller.tiktokshopglobalselling.com 的 adapter** —— 这个需要我们**自己探索生成**\n2. ✅ **`opencli browser <session> init <name>`** —— 启动方式是用 `opencli browser` 子命令,**不直接调宿主 Chrome**,这就解释了为什么叫\"独立安装\"\n3. **adapter scaffold 自动生成在 `~/.opencli/clis/`** —— 这就是你说的\"沉淀成 skill\"\n\n我现在跟你确认下一步,等你说一句再动:**完全不再碰宿主 Chrome**:\n\n| 选项 | 做什么 |\n|---|---|\n| A | 我现在用 `opencli browser init tiktokshop-seller` 起个隔离 session,探索 TK Seller 后台,生成 adapter |\n| B | 先不动 opencli,我先把今天搞错的两件事(混 dreamina-cli + 接管宿主浏览器)记到我的 ERRORS.md |\n| C | 你告诉我 opencli session 名应该叫什么 / 你想先探索哪个流程(上架/订单/改价?) |\n\n你定。\n\n[[reply_to_current"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":536,"output":237,"cacheRead":83840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84613,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782394183035,"responseId":"068c6047d3f3dfdba7a7a0001af8a1cf","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
